Am 27.02.19 um 13:10 schrieb Martin Bauer:

> Hi there,
> I am not quite sure, if this funnel plot is symmetrical and if there 
> are any bias. [...]

I would suggest that you have a look at Sterne et al. (2011).

According to the recommendations, you could conduct a linear regression 
test for funnel plot asymmetry, e.g., using regtest() in R package 
*metafor* or metabias() in *meta*.

Best wishes, Guido

Reference: Sterne JAC, Sutton AJ, Ioannidis JPA, Terrin N, Jones DR, Lau 
J, et al. Recommendations for examining and interpreting funnel plot 
asymmetry in meta-analyses of randomised controlled trials. BMJ. 
2011;343(jul22 1):d4002.

